library(dplyr)
library(tidyr)
library(ggplot2)
library(ggmap)
library(maps)

Model


set T;  # cities n
set S;  # divisions s


param d {T,T};  # distance between team u and team v
param G {S cross S};    # num of away games of team in division i v.s. team in division j
param b {i in S};   # num of teams in division S

# var x {(i,j) in E} >= 0;

var y {T,T,S,S} binary;
var x {T,S} binary;


minimize weighted_distance:
    sum{u in T, v in T, i in S, j in S} 
    y[u,v,i,j] * G[i,j] * d[u,v];

s.t. fordiv {i in S}:
    sum {v in T} x[v,i] = b[i];

s.t. forteam {v in T}:
    sum {i in S} x[v,i] = 1;

s.t. forpair_city {u in T, v in T}:
    sum {i in S, j in S} y[u,v,i,j] = 1;
    
s.t. forpair_division {i in S, j in S}:
    sum {u in T, v in T} y[u,v,i,j] = b[i]*b[j];

s.t. for_x_ui {u in T, v in T, i in S, j in S}:
    y[u,v,i,j] <= x[u,i];

s.t. for_x_vj {u in T, v in T, i in S, j in S}:
    y[u,v,i,j] <= x[v,j];

s.t. for_all {u in T, v in T, i in S, j in S}:
    y[u,v,i,j] >= x[u,i] + x[v,j] - 1;
